            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            /* ж ёеҝғдәӨдә’еҠЁз”»пјҡе№іж»‘гҖҒеҝ«йҖҹ */
            transition: all 0.2s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            border: 1px solid transparent;
